featured.text: Your dog could fall into one of nine categories: Ace, Stargazer, Maverick, Charmer, Socialite, Protodog, Einstein, Expert, or Renaissance Dog.

definition.zh_def: 社交名流，通常指在社交場合中活躍且受人矚目的人。
definition.en_def: A person who is well-known in fashionable society and is often seen at social events.
definition.example: The socialite attended all the high-profile parties in the city.
